Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language understanding and temporal relation extraction. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a new neural system for the task. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the proposed system uses contextualized word embeddings and a Siamese encoder. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is relevant as the paper proposes a neural system. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is less likely but still possible as the paper applies global inference via integer linear programming.
